author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Hilton Food Group Says Co And Woolworths Group Announce Agreement To Restructure Joint Venture​

organizations.name: woolworths group announce agreement to restructure joint venture

text:
Feb 25 (Reuters) - Hilton Food Group Plc:
* HILTON FOOD GROUP PLC: WESTERN AUSTRALIA AND VICTORIA JOINT VENTURE
* HILTON FOOD GROUP PLC SAYS CO AND WOOLWORTHS GROUP LTD ANNOUNCE AGREEMENT TO RESTRUCTURE THEIR AUSTRALIAN MEAT PROCESSING JOINT VENTURE​
* HILTON FOOD GROUP-‍AGREEMENT INCLUDES LONG TERM CONTRACTS FOR HILTON FOODS AUSTRALIA TO SUPPLY WOOLWORTHS SUPERMARKETS WITH PACKAGED & VALUE-ADDED MEAT PRODUCTS​
* HILTON FOOD GROUP- ‍AT END OF TRANSITIONAL PERIOD OF 2 YEARS, HFA WILL ACQUIRE RELEVANT PLANT ASSETS FOR A BOOK VALUE EXPECTED TO BE AU$85 MILLION Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
